title: The One Where We Just Woke Up
description:
This week on Sibling Rivalry, Jacob wakes up Bob and Monét at the crack of dawn to discuss all things sleeping. The two talk wet dreams, stank breath horror stories, nightmares, and what time they think children should go to bed. Tune in to find out whether or not you need your eyeballs to see!
